Image credit: Duane By Andile Mngxitama My dear friends, yesterday Black First Land First (BLF) launched the ‘Stop Loadshedding! Pravin Gordhan Must Go!‘ petition. Have you signed this petition yet? We need 10 000 signatures. Let’s put pressure on the president of the country, Cyril Ramaphosa, to do the right thing. Let’s make our unhappiness heard. There is no change without demands and struggle. 10 000 signatures will put moral pressure and also educate our people to take a position. Do sign the petition and share on all social media platforms. Let’s get the 10k signatures by Friday, 17 January. The Day1 target of 1000 signatures was met. Over 1500 have signed thus far. Let’s tell Ramaphosa #PravinMustGoNow Please click on the following link to sign the petition: http://chng.it/bGWxxCxN
Sign and tell others. Andile Mngxitama is the President of Black First Land First (BLF), a radical black consciousness organization No related posts.